30  rt_function_context_t *function_context) {

36  affine_local_context_t *ctx =
37  rt_malloc_func(sizeof(affine_local_context_t));
38  ctx->base_axis = f->base_axis;
39  function_context->func.local_context = ctx;
40  allocate_affine_local_context(&function_context->func);
41  } break;
42 #endif
